section.section:
The Chancellor shall:
Advise the Board of Regents on systemwide policy;
Conduct systemwide planning;
Coordinate and arbitrate among the institutions and centers of the University;
Assist the institutions in achieving performance goals in accordance with their adopted performance accountability plan;
Provide technical assistance to institutions and centers such as legal and financial services;
Perform the duties the Board assigns; and
See that the policies of the Board are carried out.
